data.description: Welcome to your future home! This 1900sqft tri-level gem, nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, beckons you to make it yours. The journey begins with a warm welcome from the covered front porch, leading you into the living room graced by a soaring cathedral ceiling, transitioning into the kitchen adorned with fresh, new flooring throughout the main level. New windows throughout home. A few steps down, you'll discover a spacious family room, complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace, and an inviting bonus room, perfect for an office or potentially a 4th bedroom, along with a convenient half bath.    The upper level is your personal haven, featuring the primary bedroom boasting a generous walk-in closet and a full bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and another full bath complete this level. Out back, revel in the expansive, fully fenced backyard, complete with a charming brick patio and landscaping ready for your personal touch. Gutter guards make for easy maintenance, and a spacious 2.5 car garage adds the finishing touch to this wonderful property. Your new home awaits!
